intent.user_query: Identify products that have not been sold in the last 6 months but have a stock quantity greater than 10. Show the product ID and current stock.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductID, p.StockQuantity FROM fitness_db.Products p WHERE p.ProductID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT ProductID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= ADD_MONTHS(CURRENT_DATE, -6)) AND p.StockQuantity > 10;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductID, p.StockQuantity FROM fitness_db.Products p WHERE p.ProductID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT ProductID FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= ADD_MONTHS(CURRENT_DATE, -6)) AND p.StockQuantity > 10;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
